olve the esophagus, leading to dysphagia.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022227,0.037254,0.050442,0.065224,0.081326,0.095484,0.10894,0.1139,0.1216,0.13165,0.10882,0.06313],"unified_progress":[0.030059,0.05415,0.072957,0.086308,0.095655,0.10971,0.10506,0.10481,0.10077,0.096038,0.080834,0.063659]},{"section":12,"text":"And those lumps could be calcinosis, which is common in certain types of scleroderma.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.016691,0.033075,0.047897,0.064188,0.081797,0.099003,0.11424,0.12107,0.13027,0.14,0.10309,0.048678],"unified_progress":[0.026346,0.052343,0.07558,0.090374,0.098593,0.10866,0.10955,0.10679,0.10147,0.095381,0.076702,0.058211]},{"section":13,"text":"Plus, the Raynaud's phenomenon fits right in with scleroderma too.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019786,0.036928,0.047864,0.058932,0.070763,0.082753,0.095461,0.10408,0.1163,0.13104,0.13367,0.10243],"unified_progress":[0.029898,0.051749,0.067113,0.078813,0.087818,0.099279,0.098744,0.10162,0.10227,0.10151,0.096651,0.084533]},{"section":14,"text":"So, putting all these pieces together\u2014the swallowing issues, the skin changes, the joint pain, and the chalky lumps\u2014it really seems like we're looking at limited scleroderma, also called CREST syndrome.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.017169,0.031247,0.041038,0.050445,0.059918,0.069854,0.081245,0.090022,0.10423,0.12831,0.1651,0.16143],"unified_progress":[0.024982,0.042208,0.054507,0.064874,0.074206,0.087682,0.090281,0.099114,0.1055,0.10967,0.12024,0.12673]},{"section":15,"text":"This syndrome includes Calcinosis, Raynaud's phenomenon, Esophageal dysmotility, Sclerodactyly, and Telangiectasia.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019183,0.031243,0.044893,0.060934,0.077322,0.093708,0.1096,0.11772,0.12919,0.14509,0.11215,0.058981],"unified_progress":[0.027008,0.049,0.069034,0.081